skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: washington business name
des: The skill allows you to check whether a company is registered in Washington state, and if registered, get a registration number. By default we search any business name that contains specified word, so if you say "Bagel", then all companies containing the word 'Bagel' in their name will be returned as a result, for example, "Red Bagel" and "Bagel Trade House". To display companies that accurately contain the specified name in the results, use the word "exact" at the end of the search phrase. for example: "Alexa, open washington business name and find bagel inc exact". You also have an options like: start with, begin with and contain. Place such predefined words at the and of the phrase.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
